long_description: our products were created as a way to sustain funding to shape the future for children through literacy and education opportunities. by importing our products from the cooperatives we are empowering women in morocco through employment and education. as a social enterprise, a door to morocco strives to support two moroccan charities in the fez community, while also providing women-led cooperatives of a fair income. every product that is sold helps to buy a new book, fund an educational field trip, or provide children with life skills that will shape their future. a door to morocco strives to support two moroccan charities, a children's library and an orphanage, while also providing an opportunity for women cooperatives to have a reliable and fair income through our products. we believe that our high-grade authentic argan oil has proven results and is derived from an ethically sourced 100% natural ingredient that will leave your skin and hair healthy, nourished and soft. we are all trying to be more mindful and live a healthier life.
